-- Fed approves discount rate cuts at three banks
-- 
-- Wed Apr 30, 2008 4:45pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/30/us-usa-fed-discountrate-idUSWBT00890420080430

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - The Federal Reserve said on Wednesday it had approved actions by the Fed banks of Kansas City, Chicago and St. Louis to lower the discount rate by a quarter percentage point to 2.25 percent. 

 The Fed earlier on Wednesday unanimously approved a cut in the discount rate to 2.25 and approved discount rate reduction requests from the Fed banks of New York, Cleveland, Atlanta, and San Francisco. (Reporting by  Mark Felsenthal )